channel.title: Are There Private "Elite" Forum On RS Cheating?
channel.description:
Do you think there are secret private communities for the "Elite" of the RuneScape coders and such.
I know there are a few secret private communities on bug abuse. One of which I am aware of know very big money making bugs at the duel arena and Wilderness.
I remember someone talking about one back at Kaitnieks, but I forgot the username.
I rekon there are a few, where people like moparisthebest and people like that go. The people who know what they are doing pretty much. Heck, perhaps kaitnieks is still in a private community somewhere.
What are your opinions and ideas?
